Venue: Marriott Marquis Hotel, 8th Floor, Times Square, New York, NY 10036. Below event in addition to Event Image. 
 Wednesday, December 09, 2015, 10pm - 11pm - Concert/Fundraiser for victims of Terrorism, including kidnapped Chibok Girls in   Nigeria. ? 
 Tickets starts at $2,000(two-thousand US Dollars) each. Sponsorship Opportunities available. Contact Soji Adeyemi at (646)258-7550 and email:  binvestmentforum2015@gmail.com 
 Limited tickets at $2,000 each and the remaining tickets will be auctioned so purchase tickets early. 
 ? 
 FAQs 
 ? 
 Are there ID requirements or an age limit to enter the event? 
 All attendees must be older than?21 years except speakers, performers and selected Celebrities like Justin Bieber. 
 ? 
 What are my transport/parking options getting to the event? 
 Attendees must find their own parking around Times Square. It is Highly recommended you take taxi or public transportation or chauvered vehicle to Times Square. 
 ? 
 What can/can't I bring to the event? 
 For security reasons, large bags are not allowed and all bags and wallets will be searched before entering the venue. 
 ? 
 Where can I contact the organizer with any questions? 
 Call Soji at (646)258-7550 or email  binvestmentforum2015@gmail.com 
 Is my registration/ticket transferrable? 
 No. Tickets are not transferable. 
 ? 
 Can I update my registration information? 
 No 
 ? 
 Do I have to bring my printed ticket to the event? 
 YES. 
 ? 
 What is the refund policy? 
 No refunds. 
 ? 
 The name on the registration/ticket doesn't match the attendee. Is that okay? 
 No
